episodes.title: Mashama Bailey
episodes.plot: Mashama Bailey returns to Georgia, her place of birth, to open a new restaurant drawing on the knowledge and culinary history of the Southern African American chefs who came before her.

episodes.title: Dario Cecchini
episodes.plot: Aspiring veterinarian Dario Ceccini returns to save his family's butchery business and becomes the world's most famous butcher.

episodes.title: Asma Khan
episodes.plot: Asma Khan abandons a career in British constitutional law to return to India to extract the secret recipes of her family's Royal Muglai roots.

episodes.title: Sean Brock
episodes.plot: Sean Brock, who has devoted his career to preserving southern food crops and culinary traditions, is finally forced to reckon with personal demons that threaten his life
